Package com.o3dr.services.android.lib.drone.companion.solo.tlv.sitescan.inspect

  • Class Summary 
    Class Description
    SoloInspectMoveGimbal
    Sent by the app to ShotManager to instruct Solo to actuate gimbal to desired orientation.
    SoloInspectMoveVehicle
    Sent by the app to ShotManager to instruct Solo to move with a certain velocity (body-relative NED frame).
    SoloInspectSetWaypoint
    Sent by the app to ShotManager to instruct Solo to navigate towards the provided waypoint.
    SoloInspectStart
    Sent by the app to ShotManager to notify that the inspect shot is ready to commence and the vehicle should climb to the provided takeoffAlt.
